    <briefdescription>
<para>Provides default guard functions for match state transitions. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Guard functions are predicates that determine whether a state transition is allowed. They are evaluated before a transition occurs and can block it by returning false.</para>
<para>All guards are static functions that take an UpdateContext and a <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1mechanics_1_1match_1_1types_1_1MatchStateTransitionRequest" kindref="compound">MatchStateTransitionRequest</ref>, returning true if the transition is allowed.</para>
